    Class Description
    ColourCalibration
    Class for EveryThing color detection related.
    Controller
    Main Class of the Robot; dictates robot behaviour.
    LightLocalizer
    Class that allows odometer Correction by using tile lines to calculate offset from theoretical position.
    Navigation
    Class containing all movement related behaviors.
    Odometer
    Class that tracks position of the robot
    OdometerData
    This class stores and provides thread safe access to the odometer data.
    Robot
    Class that contain robot constants and uses them to convert distance/turn to wheel rotation
    SearchAndLocalize
    Class that finds the needed cube in a certain rectangular area amongst other cubes
    USLocalizer
    Class that utilizes the UltraSonic Sensor to point the robot in the right direction when it is in a corner position next to two walls Utilizes falling edge and rising edge for proper localization
